description:
Addons.mozilla.org - limit description sizes (Updated)


{+} 


Addons.mozilla.org - Remove "Share This"

css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document domain("addons.mozilla.org") {

.item, .corner-box {display: block !important; outline: none !important;}

.item .first, .desc {max-height: 15em !important;}
.baseline {display: none !important;}
}


@-moz-document url-prefix(https://addons.mozilla.org/) {
.link-sharing.rollover-reveal {display: none !important} }
